<div class="_pmvv-vidbox-desc">
<h1 id="overlay-title">Yuri Undertones - Demolition D</h1>
<p id="overlay-descrip" class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Parodied hard. Demolition D gets angry at there only being Yuri Undertones rather than actual Yuri, with his rage being overly exaggerated to comedic effect.	</p>
<div class="rating-row" data-video-id="xe3m5z">
